Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:09.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このまま戻らなかったら ４人のデータ 全部　消えちゃうわね。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:09.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can no longer think of him... as a target to destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:13.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まっ　ゴレイヌからの 連絡を待つしかないな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:13.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He acknowledged our efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よし　バッチリ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He wasn't a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:22.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ねぇ　もう百発百中だよ！ 放出系の修行に集中しても いいでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:22.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In that case, I no longer have...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ダメ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}any reason to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:27.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}百発百中っつっても 誤差が０．１秒くらいあるだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:27.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:29.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}理想は　０．０１秒以内。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:29.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The soldiers are not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい　始め！ ちぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If the King waves his baton, the soldiers \Nwill become demons if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:10.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バッテラを連れて逃げたのが その証拠だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:10.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is an area used for testing weapons of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:19.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　長年かけて９６種まで カードを集めたんだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:19.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We won't need to restrain ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}推測の話をいくらしても仕方ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why do you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:35.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おっ　３時１０分　時間だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:35.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You have no chance of defeating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:38.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}イェイ！ ツェズゲラ　バイバイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:38.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why rush to your death?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:47.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３０種ぐらいは 偽物と交換してある。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:47.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You presume to know I cannot win?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:51.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}実際の９６種を抱えてるのは　俺。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:51.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You know nothing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:55.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}慎重なツェズゲラ 一世一代の大冒険だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:55.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you judge me by my appearance, you'll get burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:01.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}悪いが　ゲンスルーとお前達が 戦うことになっても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:01.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You have it backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:06.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分かってる 約束のカード　いつ取りに来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:06.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You don't seem like some ordinary man \Nwho can't read the state of the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:11.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前達がゲンスルーを 倒した後でいいさ　頑張れよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:11.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was born to rule this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:21.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}予定は狂ったが　「一坪の海岸線」も 奴らから頂こう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:21.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Originally, you humans were as \Nno more than livestock to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まずは 「アカンパニー」の調達だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I have changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:29.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ＯＫ。 奴らが動いた！ お前達　今どこだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:29.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I learned that there are a few \Nhumans worth keeping alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:34.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ソウフラビの近く。 奴らは　マサドラの方角。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:34.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Like that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:42.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}準備は　いいか？ バッチリさ あんた達のおかげだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:42.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I sense that you are worthy, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:51.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}時間が足りない でも　やるしかない あとは　ゴン次第 ゴン！ まさか　今の話に気をとられて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:51.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you back down now, I am willing to spare your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:07.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}失礼とは思いましたが 先程　拝借してまいりました。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:07.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Given my position, I can't accept that offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:22.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恋人だ。 長く入院していた。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:22.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:31.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ずっと意識がなかったが 先日　眠るように息を引き取った。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:31.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In exchange for his agreement to stay still, Pouf was pressing Pitou to explain \Njust what had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:49.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}拙い手作りの 写真立てなどを喜んだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:49.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou complied with Pouf's request, telling \Nhim what happened after the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:06:05.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一緒になろうと 誓い合った矢先だった。 事故で…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:06:05.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou made it a point to include \Ndetails that Gon did not know, to ensure that Gon's attention would \Nbe focused on the explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:10.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼女は　いつ覚めるとも分からない 眠りについた。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:10.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou deliberately did not mention \Nhow the King had held Komugi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:21.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本当に…。 ただ　眠ってるように見えた。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:21.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}because Pitou did not know how to \Ndescribe the events accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:29.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんな時 『グリードアイランド』の噂を聞いたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:29.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There was no significant change in Gon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:34.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今の私に必要な 夢のようなアイテムが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:34.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:39.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そのゲームをクリアすれば 手に入ると。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:39.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou knew the plan had succeeded \Nwhen Gon's eyes wavered briefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:46.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全財産をなげうつ覚悟で ゲームを手に入れた。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:46.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:52.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　もういい…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:52.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}left with the enemy of his own \Nvolition, by that doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もういいんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There is no need for us to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ガキどもは 全部で「アカンパニー」４回分。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see. He went south.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こっちは６枚あるし　行くか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:09.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ。 いつでもいいぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:09.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A fine play, Pitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:20.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}黒トンガリのガキは俺が相手する。 腕ずくの交渉になったらの 話だがな。 サブは　つり目　バラは女を頼む。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:20.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then we should await the King's return here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:31.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何の用だ!? そんなに　とんがるなよ 取引に来たんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:31.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To maintain only my outward appearance, \NI only need one-seventh of my flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}取引？　こっちにはないね！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The other six-sevenths
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:41.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう…　悟られてはいけない こちらが準備万端で 待ち構えていたことを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:41.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}will go to the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:59.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう　それでいい 私達は圧倒的に弱い立場を 演じなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:59.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You fight with the resolve to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの場所へは　追い詰められて たどり着いた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:06.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんな印象を 奴らに与えなければ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:06.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You fight for the human race?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:13.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}話ってのはシンプルだ。 俺達が　みんなを代表してクリアし 全員で現実へ戻り
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:13.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If so, then know that my actions \Nare, in fact, for their benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:20.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バッテラからの報酬を山分けする。 とても信じられないね。 心を入れ替えたのさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:20.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}For example, in human society, lands are divided by national borders, \Nmuch like territorial marking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:23.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}事実　ツェズゲラは もうゲームの外だぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:23.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}On the right side of the border, \Nchildren may starve to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:29.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}けど　それが　あんたらの話に 乗った証拠にはならない！ そりゃ　まぁ　そうだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:29.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}While on the left, scum who do nothing\Nhave everything they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:32.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃ　どうする…　死ぬか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:32.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Absolute madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:39.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴチャゴチャ言わずに カードをよこせ！ てめぇら全員ぶっ殺すぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:39.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I shall crush that madness...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:45.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}早速　正体　現しやがったぜ！ ブック！　「アカンパニー」オン！ ソウフラビへ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:45.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And create a world so fair, the very concept of inequality will be forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マサドラ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I will initially use power and terror \Nto accomplish my objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:14.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スペルカードを補給する気か？ 港から現実へ逃げる気かもしれん。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:14.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I will only do so to the extent \Nnecessary to maintain order. I have learned what power \Nis meant to be used for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:27.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}気配を消して隠れたか？ 店をチェックだ。 スペルカードを買われたら 厄介だからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:27.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To protect the weak, who deserve to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:32.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}来てないな。 もう港に向かったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:32.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Power is not meant to be used \Nto torment the defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:46.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見失うなよ　こっちも 「アカンパニー」は　もうない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:46.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This could be a problem... I shall not fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ…。 あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I agreed to leave the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:58.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…。 さぁ　もう諦めて カードをよこしたら　どうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:58.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}so we could have a free, open discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}嫌だね　絶対渡すもんか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's wavering...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:07.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}予想通り　奴らは マンツーマンで戦う気だわね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:07.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Come closer. Wavering between Ant and human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:11.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}渡すくらいなら　やってやる！ おい　ゴン！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:11.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And he hasn't realized
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:17.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クソ！ いいぞ　あとは少しずつ 奴らを引き離す
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:17.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that those two sides are incompatible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:20.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ビスケ！　お前は逃げろ！ でも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:20.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And neither one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:24.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いいから行け！ 待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:24.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}is dominant yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:33.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おっと　逃がさねえぞ！ 頼むよ　２人とも！ お前の相手は俺だ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:33.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But regardless of which side he falls to, the outcome won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:52.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前 俺がボマーだと知っているな？ ツェズゲラに聞いた。 ほう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:52.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The immediate extermination \Nof these dangerous creatures. There have already been many casualties. We will use any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:57.05,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}で　俺の能力は　誰に聞いた？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:57.05,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Will that be acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:02.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すごい たった一瞬の動きでバレた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:02.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Naturally, we have no intention of \Ntelling the experts how to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:06.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺が警戒していること その背景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:06.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We simply desire
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これが　戦闘経験の差！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}those dangerous creatures \Neradicated as swiftly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:12.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう多くはないはずだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:12.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:22.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の能力を知りながら 生きている奴は。 ブック！ あ？ あっちのペースに 巻き込まれちゃダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:22.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So their goal is to eradicate the Ants, \Nleaving the Hunters Association
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:26.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　問答無用でカードを奪うって やり方は嫌いだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:26.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to take the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:29.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　約束しろ 先に「参った」って言ったほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:29.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I must make this fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:34.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}持ってるカードを全部 相手に渡すって。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:34.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Before my heart is swayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは最後の譲歩だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}King...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:47.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}約束がなければ　ただの強奪。 そんな奴に 死んでもカードは渡さない！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:47.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We are both in difficult positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}器用な奴だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}100-Type Guanyin Bodhisattva!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:13:03.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　オーラの攻防力移動は かなり　お粗末 よくも　まぁ デカい口をたたいたもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:13:03.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:33.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　それは　もういい 俺が言いたいのは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:33.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}計画通り
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't sense anyone else fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:45.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}決定的な力量の差を 見せつけられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:45.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Does that mean I'm the only one left?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:48.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴をおびき寄せる行動 開始だわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:48.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Youpi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オス！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pouf!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:53.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}…って言いたいところだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:53.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You've changed a lot since I last saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:57.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やられっ放しは やっぱり　ムカつく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:57.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I could say the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:03.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}使わせてやる 作戦は　それからだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:03.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I had to escape without alerting the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:07.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フン…　もう少し痛い目に 遭いたいようだな！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:07.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And if I move all my dispersed particles \Nat once, it's too conspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:29.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チッ。 使って来い ひと泡　吹かせてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:29.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, I suppose you have your own concerns...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:34.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}…って面してるぜ 使わねえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:34.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You've grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ガキが！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have no conclusive proof
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}思ったより　すばしっこいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that the change in Pitou will \Nactually benefit the King...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:08.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「トランスフォーム」で 別のカードにしてたってことか？ 「アカンパニー」オン！ ソウフラビへ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:08.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Through his own experiences, \NYoupi could understand Pitou's behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「アカンパニー」？　なぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Youpi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:24.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何で　こんな 面倒なまねをしてまで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:24.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This was a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:28.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺とサシになりたかったのか。 理由は１つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:28.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which made it very clear to Youpi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:35.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あんたが他の２人に 助けを求めたら　面倒でしょ？ はぁ？ ますます　意味分かんねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:35.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that Pouf was fearful of the subtle changes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バカだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou and Youpi had undergone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A foolish question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハハハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We must go to the King at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:07.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}軽いねぇ　攻撃が！ おめぇには　俺は倒せねえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:07.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And that's all there is to it... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:15.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}手加減しねえぞ　恨むなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:15.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}His response was entirely sincere. Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:21.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフフ… 先に言われちゃったわね。 あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:21.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He was concerned only with \Nleaving as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:32.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}思い出に　一発 打たせてやることにしているの。 元に戻ると うまく手加減できなくて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:32.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because Youpi was feeling the same fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm sure that was a direct hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.59,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}聞いてないか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.59,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:26.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}体術や筋力は　俺がやや上 だけど　オーラの量は はるかに俺が劣る
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:26.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A good attack. I could not anticipate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:30.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}通常の攻撃じゃ 恐らくダメージは与えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:30.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:41.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ！ クソっ　拳の痛みが 頭の芯まで響く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:41.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He still wants me to sit with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}余裕こいてる暇ねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I shall not repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:12.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも数秒は 動きを止められるな ＯＫ　実験　その２
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:12.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Third Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:21.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}行くぜ。 何を仕込んでやがる…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:21.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can no longer back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:41.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の兄貴に特注した 超合金ヨーヨー。 重さ５０ｋｇくらいあるから 食らったら　効くぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:41.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you really so eager to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クソっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}From the King's perspective, the wrath that was unleashed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:55.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}遠心力と重さで　とんでもねえ 攻撃力になってやがる！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:55.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}was no stronger than that \Nof a child throwing a fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:02.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴は　俺が特定の攻撃を 仕掛けた時　必ず右側が空く
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:02.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yet it was violent enough to induce \NNetero to more than double the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヨーヨーを奪い 奴の両手をフリーにすれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}between the King and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:11.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その癖は　必ず顔を出す！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:11.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It was an insult likened to laughing off
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:15.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！　チッ！ 勝機！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:15.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Netero's declaration that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そこだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}he would not back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よし！　あばら粉砕コース！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:31.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ！ あれ？　ヨーヨー２個あるって 言わなかったっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:31.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You will only influence me by using words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damned newborn brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:44.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}う…。 うわっ　まだ意識あんの？ おっさんさ　蹴る時 反対側の腕のガード上がるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:44.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If it were that simple, \NI wouldn't have to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その死角を利用して
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:53.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヨーヨーを取り出し 攻撃したってのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:53.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}By using...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:56.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それじゃ　お前の防御の癖も？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:56.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}words?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:59.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}左足のミドルを 誘うためのフェイク。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:59.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}King...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:01.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１個目のヨーヨーを 離したのも…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:01.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Would you like to know your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:10.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「アカンパニー」で 仲間から離れたのは？ １対１を意識させて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:10.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How would you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:22.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}信じられねえ　今の短い攻防で ３つも罠を仕掛けやがるとは。 ３つ？　冗談だろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:22.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My subordinates were present at the \Nmoment of your mother's passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:26.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}動き全てが罠だぜ。 うわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:26.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She uttered your name with her dying breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:34.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ!! 実験終了！　どっちもいけるね。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:34.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And my subordinates may have died \Nfighting your Royal Guard by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:42.55,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いいかげん　認めたらどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:42.55,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Interested in fighting me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:51.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全然　俺は… 参ってない！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:51.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you can force me to admit defeat, I will tell you your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:57.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　勘違いしてたな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:57.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Force you to admit defeat without killing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:08.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の能力…　お見せしよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:08.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So, similar to a bishop and rook handicap...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:30.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝つためなら 意地を捨て　理をとる！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:30.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}悟らせてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I shall checkmate you shortly.
